{"tid":1881987,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府部門之冠 警獲發1.3萬個N95 衞署不足300","createTime":"2020-02-16T02:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T03:47:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74c4c12380cf0f10740ac803e8e3f8f0328bc5b4","tid":1881987,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200216/BDKZNCIJKNRQGMCREQHI3U52FA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200216%2FBDKZNCIJKNRQGMCREQHI3U52FA%2F&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx%2FE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=3307053d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200216%2FBDKZNCIJKNRQGMCREQHI3U52FA%2F&h=955ae3ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200216/BDKZNCIJKNRQGMCREQHI3U52FA/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府部門之冠<br />\n警獲發1.3萬個N95 衞署不足300<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】刻下全民都為着口罩苦惱，除了為特首林鄭月娥打江山的一批心腹愛將。《蘋果》取得文件，政府物流署首輪分配物資時，警方獲發近64萬個外科口罩、1.3萬個N95口罩，更預期需要逾4萬件全身防護衣。本身是醫生的立法會議員郭家麒批評，防疫資源分配不公，警方得到大批高級防疫裝備，真正接觸病人的醫護卻沒有足夠的N95口罩和防護衣，「極之浪費資源，嘥咗公帑，令已經好緊絀嘅防護衣物更加短缺」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果》取得文件，在首輪分配中，負責防控疫情的衞生署獲發最多外科口罩，數量達131萬個。過去大半年來全力打壓示威的警務處排名第二，獲發近64萬個。N95口罩方面，警方獲發1.3萬個，是眾部門之冠，衞生署僅獲分配不足300個N95。警方更預期，2月至4月需要2.6萬件保護袍（Gown）、逾4萬件全身防護衣（Protective Coverall Suit）。相比之下，衞生署只預期需要7萬件保護袍，2,000多件全身防護衣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200216/large/1581785279_ada7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200216%2Flarge%2F1581785279_ada7.gif&h=f8bfad6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前青衣康美樓有住戶確診，警方到場穿起高級保護衣自拍，被轟浪費裝備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n索4萬全身防護衣<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：病毒可隨人員衣物被帶出實驗室<br />\n<br />\n其他紀律部隊獲發裝備都沒警方優厚。市政清潔部門如食環署，獲發外科口罩僅及警方一半。近日警方多次出勤時，佩戴全套保護裝備，已被外界質疑其防護規格較醫護人員更高。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員郭家麒指，警方獲發外科口罩尚可理解，但N95、全身防護衣屬全球緊缺的防護裝備，是醫護人員處理受感染病人使用。他質問：「警察幾何要對住病人？」警方獲發高級防護裝備，變相令真正有需要的人欠缺裝備，做法十分自私。<br />\n<br />\n新公務員工會主席顏武周指，政府一直無公開分配給各部門防護裝備的數量。工會曾收到不同部門公務員投訴，例如有房署職員巡查喉管時欠缺防護裝備，有消防員投訴收到過期的N95，亦有滲水辦員工做檢測時不獲發裝備。<br />\n<br />\n他指，警方獲發第二多外科口罩，令人質疑分配準則，「憑咩排第二？救護、消防比佢哋更前線」。工會曾致函公務員事務局，查詢派發裝備的準則。局方僅稱警方要站崗和協助突擊檢查，裝備合理。<br />\n<br />\n本報向政府物流署查詢分配多少防疫裝備予警方、準則是甚麼，以及警方獲分配防疫物資數量，至昨晚截稿時未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n政府fb公關專頁添馬台昨晚回應稱：「最簡單的理由是因為警隊人數達30,000人，是各部門人數之最。警隊亦一直協助衞生署執行防疫工作，包括：在檢疫中心駐守、駐守口岸協助執行檢疫令、突擊檢查在家受檢疫人士等。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200216/large/1581785279_f2b8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200216%2Flarge%2F1581785279_f2b8.gif&h=8523608b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7d92ba9b905babd078a2d12a471645bab73ff0c","tid":1881987,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yr7iwuR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYr7iwuR.jpg&h=f4c1d23c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Qk79gx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Qk79gx.jpg&h=b818c8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wwe8TJg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwe8TJg.gif&h=ba189959&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a0ab0c4d263a1678c68928dfb52c32be89d580c","tid":1881987,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d92ba9b905babd078a2d12a471645bab73ff0c","tid":1881987,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yr7iwuR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYr7iwuR.jpg&h=f4c1d23c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Qk79gx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Qk79gx.jpg&h=b818c8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wwe8TJg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwe8TJg.gif&h=ba189959&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437529986932e986ce0b6b7ef87af91ae8a63d4d","tid":1881987,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"醫護人多定警犬狗多？<br />\n醫護唔夠警犬前線？？<br />\n<br />\n咁交比警犬去做啦"},{"pid":"b919abfdb685321bd35b4c9b0a3abf56934fe3e7","tid":1881987,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}